content: Yeah, I've been using Fetch Rewards for a few months now, and it's been pretty good. I've already earned 3,000 points, which is equivalent to $30. But anyway, back to my grocery shopping. Speaking of which, I recently redeemed 500 points from SaveMore for a $5 discount on my last grocery bill, which is equivalent to a $5 gift card. It's nice to get those little perks!
